(4767, 299, 'accordion_section_1_accordion_content', 'Certain species are adapted for the conditions found in riparian areas. Preference should always be given to native or at least non-invasive species.\r\n\r\n<i>(Adapted from Harris, n.d., Beneficial management practices for riparian zones in Atlantic Canada)</i>'),
